      I'm currently a dual student of <strong>Computer Science (B.Sc.)</strong> and work as a <strong>Systems Engineer</strong>. This means I spend a lot of time with hardware, infrastructure, and various technical challenges. In my daily work and personal projects, I often encounter problems that aren't well documented online. Sometimes you just have to figure things out the hard way.
